	impressions		CDATA		#IMPLIED
	country			CDATA		#IMPLIED
	region			CDATA		#IMPLIED
	accesstype		(I|E|P|X)	#REQUIRED
	source_rank		CDATA		#IMPLIED
	webrank			CDATA		#IMPLIED
>
<!--
	Element			source		required
	Description		Newspaper name, website name, broadcast company etc

	id			Unique numeric ID for the sourc: Retriever's SourceId's will be continued. MASE will have to assign SourceId's for each source using number from 50000 onwards. MANO will have to assign SourceId's for each of their sources using number from 55000 onwards.
	name			Full name of source
	category		Regional, national, "fagblad" (english?),
	impressions		Number of items printed
	country			ISO country code, where published, Using ISO 3166 A2 upper case  codes
	region			Region code, where published. We will have to develop a coding scheme as we go. For Norway we may use things like NOF03 (fylke) and NOK0301 (kommune) (Oslo).  Include broader terms if any.
	accesstype		Internal/External
	source_rank		
	webrank			
-->


